title: Episode 343: Global Options (Feat. AJ Johnson)
itunes:title: Episode 343: Global Options (Feat. AJ Johnson)
description:
AJ Johnson is BACK...but this time to expand and clear some things up after her last interview went viral. Aside from the threesome, the ladies discuss topics including: what remains on their sexual bucket list, how important are looks in the relationship, secrets that one is afraid to share with their partner, and much more, Enjoy!
